 (2012) that will transcend the Painted Bits of GUIs (Graphical User Interfaces), the current dominant paradigm of HCI (Human-Computer Interaction)."}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300","children":["This is an academic homepage template for researchers, built with Next.js, Tailwind CSS, and ShadcnUI. The homepage is designed to showcase your research, projects, and publications. ",["$","a",null,{"className":"underline hover:text-neutral-900 dark:hover:text-neutral-50","href":"https://github.com/anxndsgn/academic-homepage-template","children":"View on GitHub"}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300","children":["$","a",null,{"className":"underline hover:text-neutral-900 dark:hover:text-neutral-50","href":"https://zeabur.com?referralCode=anxndsgn&utm_source=anxndsgn&utm_campaign=oss","children":["$","img",null,{"src":"https://zeabur.com/deployed-on-zeabur-light.svg","alt":"Deployed on Zeabur"}]}]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"flex flex-col gap-3","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-semibold","children":"News"}],["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100","children":"2024/03/01"}]," - Two paper got accepted at CHI 2024"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100","children":"2024/03/01"}]," - I'm a news article"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100","children":"2024/03/01"}]," - I'm a news article"]}],"\n"]}]]}],"$undefined","$undefined"]}]],null],null]},[["$","html",null,{"lang":"en","children":